Allows users of booklove to download their data securely to be gdpr compliant. 
Will be implemented when I have access to Heroku again :)


## db structure

CREATE TABLE user_data_download_links (
    id UUID PRIMARY KEY DEFAULT gen_random_uuid(),
    user_id UUID NOT NULL,
    download_key TEXT UNIQUE NOT NULL,
    created_at TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
    expires_at TIMESTAMP NOT NULL
);